        {
            "title": "美勞工部長查韋斯-德雷默將離任 因涉與工作人員存在不當關係遭調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"勞工部\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:勞工部;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/勞工部\">勞工部</a>長洛麗·查韋斯-德雷默即將離任，成為川普在中期選舉前重組團隊過程中離職的最新內閣成員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮通訊主任Steven Cheung周一在社交媒體上發帖稱，「勞工部長洛麗·查韋斯-德雷默將離開政府，前往私營部門任職。」Steven Cheung稱現任勞工部副部長Keith Sonderling將擔任該部門代理部長一職。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">查韋斯-德雷默因被指與一名工作人員存在不當關係、涉嫌差旅欺詐以及在工作場所飲酒而成為勞工部監察長辦公室的調查對象。白宮在調查初期曾為她辯護，新聞秘書卡羅琳·萊維特表示，川普認為查韋斯-德雷默的工作「非常出色」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e7b0b270-823f-3b4a-8be2-3533c4fb0016-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一份提交給監察長的投訴指控高級助手捏造出差行程，以便讓部長有時間陪伴家人和朋友。查韋斯-德雷默還被指控多次邀請一名工作人員到其酒店房間。在勞工部監察長調查這些指控期間，幾名助手已被安排行政休假。勞工部否認了這些指控。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著11月中期選舉臨近，川普所在的共和黨在保住對國會控制方面挑戰艱巨，查韋斯-德雷默是近期內閣成員離職潮中的最新一位。民調顯示，選民對川普的經濟議程不滿情緒升溫，大多數選民也不認可他對伊朗戰爭的處理方式。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Labor Chief Chavez-DeRemer to Leave Post, White House Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E6%9F%A5%E9%9F%8B%E6%96%AF-%E5%BE%B7%E9%9B%B7%E9%BB%98%E5%B0%87%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%BB-%E5%9B%A0%E6%B6%89%E8%88%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E9%81%AD%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-221105753.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 07:05:31",
