        {
            "title": "庫克卸任蘋果執行長,任內市值成長逾1000%;約翰·特納斯接任",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RcEWscWp_ReqFGoQO.VVPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED2K0FV_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 蘋果(NASDAQ:AAPL)股價在週一盤後下跌逾1%,此前該公司宣布提姆·庫克將轉任執行董事長,約翰·特納斯將於2026年9月1日起接任執行長一職。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項獲得蘋果董事會一致通過的領導層變動令投資者感到意外。庫克將繼續擔任執行長至夏季,以便與特納斯密切合作完成交接。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特納斯目前擔任硬體工程資深副總裁,於2001年加入蘋果產品設計團隊,並於2013年晉升為硬體工程副總裁。他於2021年加入高階主管團隊,負責監督多條產品線的硬體工程工作,包括iPad、AirPods、iPhone、Mac和<span><span><span><span>蘋果</span></span></span></span>手錶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-56b22069-b641-3231-b9c0-a325badfa488-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">擔任執行董事長後,庫克將協助公司處理特定事務,包括與全球政策制定者進行交流。過去15年擔任蘋果非執行董事長的亞瑟·萊文森將於2026年9月1日起擔任首席獨立董事。特納斯將於同日加入董事會。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">庫克於2011年接任執行長,在其任內帶領蘋果從市值約3,500億美元成長至4萬億美元,增幅超過1,000%。年度營收從2011財年的1,080億美元成長近四倍,達到2025財年的逾4,160億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在特納斯任職期間,他在推出多條新產品線方面發揮了關鍵作用,並帶領公司專注於可靠性和耐用性。他擁有賓州大學機械工程學士學位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於這項消息,Wedbush科技分析師丹·艾夫斯表示,投資者對此可能會抱持複雜心態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"投資者會認為這是好壞參半的消息,因為突然轉任執行董事長顯然是高層推動變革的結果,\"艾夫斯評論道。\"這將是一雙難以填補的大鞋,庫克在此時退出執行長職位可能有其道理,但也引發了疑問。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">艾夫斯強調,蘋果正在經歷人工智慧方向的重大轉變,這使得庫克的意外離任更加引人注目。外界對於強而有力的人工智慧策略期望不斷升高,庫克可能認為在WWDC之前基礎已經奠定,使得此刻成為交棒的合理時機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"庫克在庫比蒂諾留下了持久的遺產,特納斯將面臨巨大壓力,需要從一開始就取得成功,尤其是在人工智慧方面,\"該分析師繼續說道。\"雖然先前有傳聞庫克將卸任執行長,但投資者目前對於時機選擇以及這對蘋果整體策略的意義會有更多疑問而非答案。這將給蘋果帶來更大壓力,要求其在WWDC上展示成功並公布產品路線圖,而人工智慧將成為核心焦點。\"</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7-%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A7%E5%B8%82%E5%80%BC%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E9%80%BE1000-%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0-%E7%89%B9%E7%B4%8D%E6%96%AF%E6%8E%A5%E4%BB%BB-213844650.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 05:44:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞馬遜將向Anthropic追加50億美元投資",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 兩家公司表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"亞馬遜\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/亞馬遜\">亞馬遜</a>將向<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a> PBC追加投資50億美元，並計畫隨著時間推移將其投資規模擴大至多達200億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic開發Claude聊天機器人和編程工具，計畫在未來十年內在亞馬遜的雲技術和晶片上投入超過1000億美元。亞馬遜是Anthropic主要投資方之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Amazon to Invest an Additional $5 Billion in Anthropic</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9536c699-c022-36ed-a285-c36c1a2d06be-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
